OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening but staying
OL,7,Fmostly cloudy with a few clear
OL,8,Fintervals breaking through. Mostly dry
OL,9,Fovernight with some clear spells in
OL,10,Fthe east, thicker cloud and patchy
OL,11,Frain in the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FPatchy light rain at first
OL,14,Fthrough the Trossachs and west.
OL,15,FOtherwise, bright or sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping and feeling quite warm in
OL,17,Fany sunshine. Winds light or moderate
OL,18,Ffrom the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
